#Testing the knowledge of Hoisting concepts

#Problem:

function x() {
    setTimeout(function () {
        console.log(i);
    }, 1000);

    var i = 1;
}

x();


#Output: 1(after one second)

#Explainaition:
- Concept of Hoisting 
- Check only var is hoisting or anything else like let, const 
- check also if anything like function in JS also hoiting 
- check which all not hoiting in JS
- Check how hoisted var, function stacked and executing in the order

#Slight changes can be made and asked here in sometimes:

function x() {

   var i = 1;

    setTimeout(function () {
        console.log(i);
    }, 1000);

   
}

x();
